			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1516727">
									

<p>My interpretation is that 053 would've turned into, well, what she is <em>anyway</em>, but the accident just coincided with when her properties began to manifest. Correlation is not causation, after all.</p>
<p>Which actually leads to a more disturbing realization that we, as human beings, are so desperate for there to be a <em>reason</em> for things being the way they are that we immediately jump to conclusions instead of being willing to say &quot;there is no meaning behind this, it just is.&quot;</p>

